doctorInfo.title: MEET OUR DOCTOR
doctorInfo.subtitle: Best Skin Specialist and Best Aesthetic Dermatologist
doctorInfo.name: DR.Muhammad Kabir
doctorInfo.about_1: If you’re concerned about a dermatological issue, let us help. Whether your concern involves acne, a rash, or skin cancer removal, we can ensure the healthy skin you deserve.
doctorInfo.about_2: Facial wrinkles, frown lines, crows’ feet, age spots, or a tattoo you are not happy with? We can help, and we have the full range of services you’re seeking.
doctorInfo.about_3: Now is the time to take care of yourself. Give yourself the gift of health this holiday season with no, to little to no out-of-pocket expense.

clinicInfo.title: INTRODUCTION
clinicInfo.name: Multan Aesthetics
clinicInfo.about_1: This clinic has officially proven to have a level of expertise, facilities, services & patient responses well above current international clinic standards.
clinicInfo.about_2: The clinic staff (Dermatology) includes range of specialists from variety of departments such as Dermatology and Aesthetic Dermatology
clinicInfo.about_3: Languages spoken at the clinic include , English, Urdu and Saraiki.

home.subtitle: Care Your Beauty
home.description: Skin care and medical treatments to address specific skin concerns are becoming ever more sophisticated. There’s now an array of non-invasive procedures available to deal with a wide range of skin issues – from sun damage and wrinkles to hyperpigmentation, acne scars and more.

points.title: 7 Years Of Dermatology Experience
points.description: Highly-skilled & experienced dermatologist. Adults & kids welcome. Medical, surgical and cosmetic dermatology care.

points.title: A Leader In Dermatologic Care
points.description: we are proud to be experts in the most advanced dermatological treatments for a wide range of skin conditions. Whether you have acne, skin cancer or a cosmetic skin care concern, our team of award winning physicians and staff is ready to assist you.

points.title: Clinical Dermatology Research
points.description: At Multan Aesthetics Clinic, the Department of Dermatology provides top-line clinical care to patients with all stages of skin diseases.
